keyword.prompt:
TASK: Identify words or short phrases in the text that relate to each label.

INPUT DETAILS:
- Text: "${text}"
- Annotation task: ${description}
- Available labels: ${labels}

INSTRUCTIONS:
For each label, find words or short phrases from the text that indicate or relate to that label. Only include words/phrases that actually appear in the text. Return 1-5 keywords per label. If no words relate to a label, return an empty list for that label.

EXAMPLE OUTPUT FORMAT:
{"label_keywords": [{"label": "positive", "keywords": ["great", "love it"]}, {"label": "negative", "keywords": ["terrible"]}]}
